summary:
From 2016-2018, I ran a blog that focused on professional wrestling in North Carolina titled Wrestling with My Thoughts.  It was a small blog that consisted of recaps from live events I attended and my suggestions for improvements. 
In March of 2017, AML Wrestling (the organization I attended the most live events) came to Franklin, North Carolina, just a short drive from where I lived...
title: Interviewing Jax Dane (RIP)
